# 🎨 Flow Design System — Complete UI Audit
> **MyProfile** · Extracted from source · No redesign, analysis only

---

## 1. 🎨 COLOR SYSTEM

### Token Map (from `variables.css`)

| Token | Value | Role |
|---|---|---|
| `--bg-base` | `#0c0c0c` | Root background, app shell |
| `--bg-surface` | `#111111` | Card surfaces (tags, QR area) |
| `--bg-hover` | `#161616` | Hover fill for drop zones, pwd menu |
| `--bg-active` | `#1c1c1c` | Active/pressed states, avatar bg, btn-primary bg |
| `--bg-input` | `#141414` | All form inputs / textareas |
| `--border-default` | `#222222` | Standard borders (cards, inputs, tags) |
| `--border-subtle` | `#191919` | Dividers, separator lines |
| `--border-accent` | `#383838` | Focused input borders, scrollbar thumb, footer dot |
| `--text-primary` | `#e4e4e4` | Headings, active labels, focused content |
| `--text-secondary` | `#7a7a7a` | Default body text, row labels, tags |
| `--text-muted` | `#404040` | Metadata, counts, preview text, disabled states |
| `--text-inverse` | `#0c0c0c` | Text on light/accent backgrounds (unused in current UI) |
| `--accent` | `#b8956a` | Warm amber — primary accent, lock icon, copy btn, link btn |
| `--accent-dim` | `rgba(184,149,106,0.12)` | Accent hover fill, `::selection` background |
| `--accent-hover` | `#c9a87c` | Accent hover state (btn-copy hover) |

### Hardcoded Colors (Outside Token System)

| Value | Location | Role |
|---|---|---|
| `#e05252` | btn-danger, lock-error, pwd-error, row-action-btn--danger | Error / destructive red |
| `#b05252` | btn-ghost-danger default state | Softer danger (dimmed) |
| `#3a2222` | btn-ghost-danger border, pwd-reset-icon border | Danger border (dark red tint) |
| `rgba(224,82,82,0.06)` | pwd-error bg, btn-ghost-danger:hover bg | Error fill (very dim) |
| `#5aba8a` | pwd-success__icon border + color | Success green |
| `rgba(12,12,12,0.98)` | mobile-tab-bar background | Mobile bar blur bg |
| `rgba(255,255,255,0.35)` | .tab-btn (inactive) | Mobile tab inactive color |
| `rgba(0,0,0,0.6)` | .edit-overlay backdrop | Modal scrim |
| `#141414` | .edit-modal background | Modal surface (duplicates `--bg-input`) |
| `#111111` | .share-qr background | QR surface (duplicates `--bg-surface`) |
| `#ffffff` | .tab-btn--active | Active tab label (pure white) |
| `#b8956a` | .tab-btn--active::before | Active indicator line (restates `--accent`) |

### Color Groups

**Primary (backgrounds)**
- Base: `#0c0c0c` → Surface: `#111111` → Input: `#141414` → Hover: `#161616` → Active: `#1c1c1c`

**Borders**
- Subtle → Default → Accent: `#191919` → `#222222` → `#383838`

**Text hierarchy**
- Muted → Secondary → Primary: `#404040` → `#7a7a7a` → `#e4e4e4`

**Accent (warm amber)**
- Dim → Default → Hover: `rgba(184,149,106,0.12)` → `#b8956a` → `#c9a87c`

**State Colors (hardcoded, no tokens)**
- Error: `#e05252` / `#b05252` / `#3a2222`
- Success: `#5aba8a`

### ⚠️ Issues Found
- `--text-inverse` token is defined but **never used** anywhere in the codebase
- `#141414` used directly in `.edit-modal` — duplicates `--bg-input` without token
- `#111111` used directly in `.share-qr` — duplicates `--bg-surface` without token
- `#b8956a` is restated in `.tab-btn--active::before` — should use `var(--accent)`
- Error/Success colors have **no design tokens** defined (`--color-error`, `--color-success`)

