## 4. 🧱 BORDER & SHAPE SYSTEM

### Border Widths

| Width | Usage |
|---|---|
| `1px` | **Universal** — every border in the system is 1px |
| `2px` | `.pwd-error` left accent bar, `.pwd-remove-note` left bar, strength-bar segments |
| `4px` | Scrollbar width and height |

### Border Styles

| Style | Usage |
|---|---|
| `solid` | All card, input, modal, row, tag borders |
| `dashed` | `.drop-zone`, `.btn-add-group` |
| `none` | Reset on `button` elements |

### Border Colors by Token

| Context | Token |
|---|---|
| Default cards, inputs, tags | `--border-default` (`#222222`) |
| Dividers, row separators | `--border-subtle` (`#191919`) |
| Focus states, scrollbar | `--border-accent` (`#383838`) |
| Accent hover | `var(--accent)` |
| Danger borders | `#3a2222` |

### Border Radius Values

| Token / Value | Usage |
|---|---|
| `--radius: 2px` | All inputs, tags (from reset.css) |
| `--radius-sm: 1px` | Defined but **not used** in any current selector |
| `2px` | Scrollbar thumb radius |
| `50%` | `.lock-dot` (circles) |
| `0` | Section rows, item rows (explicitly `border-radius: 0`) |

### Shape Character

- **Predominantly sharp/square**: The whole system defaults to `0` or `2px` radius.
- `--radius-sm (1px)` is defined but unused.
- Only the lock-screen dot is perfectly round (`50%`).
- No card or panel uses a visible corner radius.
- **Very consistent** — no rogue border-radii found.

