## 5. 🎯 ICON SYSTEM

### Icon Library

**Lucide React** — imported per-component, no global icon registry.

### Icon Sizes Used

| Size | Used In |
|---|---|
| `12px` | Row action icons (Pencil, Trash2), detail-link-btn icons, btn-ghost icons |
| `13px` | Header actions (Share2, Lock, LockOpen, RotateCcw), item-row arrow (ChevronRight), section-row (ChevronRight), identity-edit-btn (Pencil), btn-add icon (Plus) |
| `14px` | Section-row ChevronRight |
| `20px` | Mobile tab bar icons (Home, Share2, Settings2), header back button (ChevronLeft) |
| Variable | `Globe`, `Video`, `ExternalLink` in detail links |

### Stroke Width

| Value | Usage |
|---|---|
| Default (`~2`) | All header/action icons |
| `1.75` | Mobile tab bar icons (explicitly set for lighter appearance) |

### Filled vs Outline
All icons use **outline style** (Lucide default). No filled icon variants are used.

### Icon Usage by Context

| Context | Icons Used |
|---|---|
| Navigation | `ChevronLeft`, `ChevronRight` |
| Header actions | `Share2`, `Lock`, `LockOpen`, `RotateCcw` |
| Edit / CRUD | `Pencil`, `Trash2`, `Plus` |
| Mobile tab bar | `Home`, `Share2`, `Settings2` |
| Detail links | `Globe`, `Video`, `ExternalLink` |
| Links section | `ExternalLink` (link rows) |
| Auth | `Lock`, `LockOpen` |
| QR / share error | Implied (no explicit icon named in code, just error state) |

